'''長臂天牛'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Acrocinus longimanus''}}）為[[天牛科|天牛科]][[粗天牛亞科|粗天牛亞科]]的動物。分布於[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲地區]]（北起[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]，南至[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]北部）的熱帶雨林<ref name="Tavakilian">{{cite web | url = http://lully.snv.jussieu.fr/titan/sel_genann1.php?numero=173 | title = ''Acrocinus longimanus'' (Linné, 1758) | author = Cerambycidae database. Tavakilian G | accessdate = 2009-05-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140426233000/http://lully.snv.jussieu.fr/titan/sel_genann1.php?numero=173 | archivedate = 2014-04-26 }}</ref>。雄蟲前肢特長，屬於大型天牛，體長可達約 7.6 公分<ref name = "id708166">"[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/708166/harlequin-beetle Harlequin beetle]". in [[大英百科全書|Encyclopædia Britannica]] Online. Encyclopædia Britannica, 2011. Accessed 24 Jan 2011.</ref>。

與少數種類的[[擬蠍目|擬蠍]]具有[[偏利共生|偏利共生]]的關係（已知有三種，分別是 ''Cordylochernes scorpioides''<ref>{{cite journal | author = Höfer H., L. Beck | title = "Die Spinnentierfauna des Regenwaldreservats "Reserva Ducke" in Zentralamazonien I" | journal = ''Natur und Museum'' | volume = 125 | pages = 389–401 | year = 1995 | url = }}</ref>, ''Lustrochernes intermedius'' 與 ''Parachelifer lativittatus''<ref>{{cite journal | author = Aguiar Nair Otaviano, Buhrnheim Paulo Friedrich | title = "Phoretic pseudoscorpions associated with flying insects in Brazilian Amazônia" | journal = ''The Journal of Arachnology'' | volume = 26 | pages = 452–459 | year = 1998 | url = http://www.americanarachnology.org/joa_free/joa_v26_n3/joa_v26_p452.pdf }}</ref>）<ref name = "Tavakilian"/><ref>{{cite book | author = Henderson, Carrol L. | title = "Butterflies, Moths, and Other Invertebrates of Costa Rica: A Field Guide" | publisher = ''University of Texas Press'' | year = 2010 | page = pp.130 | isbn = 0-292-71966-3 | url = http://books.google.com.tw/books?id=gris_x5dnF0C&printsec=frontcover&hl=zh-TW&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>，擬蠍會短時間的附著在長臂天牛身上，藉由長臂天牛移動而達到移動至他處的目的。

在英文中被稱為「Harlequin beetle」，亦即「滑稽的甲蟲」，形容甲殼上的花紋，像小丑身上的衣服；種名「''longimanus''」在拉丁文是指「長的手」<ref name = "id708166"/>；形容雄蟲細長的前肢。

